Package: NEClasFlows
Title: Tools to Analyze Cross-National Reporting and Entity Flows
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Tobias", "Schmidt", email = "tobias3.schmidt@tu-dortmund.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Helpers for cleaning, aggregating and visualizing reporting flows across countries and entity classes. Provides article-level matrices, monthly aggregations, thresholded hit counts, and publication-ready plots.
